## UX Metrics & Success Criteria

### MVP Success Metrics

 | Metric | Target | Measurement |
 | ------ | ------ | ----------- |
 | First game completion rate | > 40% | Analytics: % of users who finish first game |
 | Charleston tutorial skip rate | < 20% | Track "Skip Tutorial" clicks |
 | Mobile drop-off rate | < 30% | Compare mobile vs. desktop completion rates |
 | Average session length | 15-20 min | Track time from join to leave |
 | Reconnection success rate | > 90% | % of disconnects that successfully rejoin |

### Post-MVP Metrics

- **Pattern viability adoption**: % of users who enable auto-graying

- **Keyboard shortcut usage**: % of experienced players using hotkeys

- **Mobile one-handed mode**: % of mobile users enabling thumb-zone layout

- **Accessibility usage**: % of sessions with screen reader detected

